00:35:41.440 --> 00:35:44.470 align:middle line:90%
I say, no, no, no.

00:35:44.470 --> 00:35:48.230 align:middle line:84%
It is a million angels singing
glory to God in the highest.

00:35:48.230 --> 00:35:50.040 align:middle line:90%
Hallelujah.

00:35:50.040 --> 00:35:51.880 align:middle line:84%
Now in ordinary
Aristotelian logic,

00:35:51.880 --> 00:35:53.340 align:middle line:84%
