00:36:00.530 --> 00:36:04.360 align:middle line:90%
singing glory, glory, et cetera.

00:36:04.360 --> 00:36:07.170 align:middle line:90%
I don't think we have to choose.

00:36:07.170 --> 00:36:09.280 align:middle line:84%
If you want to do
18th century science,

00:36:09.280 --> 00:36:10.430 align:middle line:90%
consider it a burning rock.

00:36:10.430 --> 00:36:12.220 align:middle line:84%
If you want to
write good poetry,

00:36:12.220 --> 00:36:15.240 align:middle line:90%
consider it a band of angels.

00:36:15.240 --> 00:36:18.370 align:middle line:84%
What matters is your purpose
and how your perceptions

00:36:18.370 --> 00:36:19.950 align:middle line:90%
suit your purpose.

00:36:19.950 --> 00:36:23.210 align:middle line:84%
I believe Blake did see
